reviewText: It was no surprise that my 5 yr old son would love this Dora episode; he has watched this over and over again, but never gets tired of it. I'm very pleased with this purchase. I'm sure glad I purchased this title and so is he.
I'd like to know which episodes are on this one before I buy it, but they don't list that information in the description.  Does anyone know?
The DVD I bought was used and had scratches on it, the seller immediatly replaced a brand new one for me. I love their services and will surely buy from them again.
You can't go wrong with Dora for your little ones- she encourages learing, verbal and spatial.  My little girl loves this video, so will yours.

GREAT DVD, MY GRANDDAUGHTER LOVES IT AND CAN'T WATCH IT ENOUGH.

THANKS SO MUCH

Another one of the great Dora DVDs. My kids love it and want to watch it over and over again!. The two spy episodes encouraged my kids to role play being spies and made their own spy gadgets. Endless hours of fun and entertainment :)
My 23 month old daughter just loves Dora. Though she's not quite saying two words together, she definitely repeats what she see's on her tv. Keeps her tuned in while I do chores.

movie is great for little girls and boys, my grandaughter loves all new dora's, it teaches them love, to help and be honest.
we own every dora movie ever made.
you have to buy dora undercover.
It was awesome! My autistic daughter watches it over and over...she is the only one in her Spanish class at school that knew spanish before school started!

If you have a grand daughter, this is a must for your video collection.  Lots of good educational material combined with some movement, questions, and activities.  Overall a good item to have on the shelf for down time or a rainy afternoon.
